6. Notes and Known issues
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    I'd also suggest to add a file into your $HOME/ftdetect called txt.vim that
    contains a line: 
      au BufRead,BufNewFile *  setfiletype txt

    It sets your syntax to txt if no syntax was found before.

